78416:1908010901:0059/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn85042242/1908-01-09/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "rights": ["<p>The Library of Congress believes that the newspapers in Chronicling America are in the public domain or have no known copyright restrictions.  Newspapers published in the United States more than 95 years ago are in the public domain in their entirety. Any newspapers in Chronicling America that were published less than 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.332207, "shard": "07", "shelf_id": "sn85042242, 1908-01-09, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/ndhi", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["bismarck", "newspapers", "north dakota", "bismarck (n.d.)", "united states", "burleigh"], "subject_headings": ["Bismarck (N.D.)--Newspapers", "North Dakota--Bismarck", "United States--North Dakota--Burleigh--Bismarck"], "subjects": [{"bismarck": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:bismarck&fo=json"}, {"bismarck (n.d.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:bismarck+%28n.d.%29&fo=json"}, {"burleigh": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:burleigh&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"north dakota": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:north+dakota&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2023-08-26T00:21:13.748Z", "title": "Bismarck daily tribune (Bismarck, Dakota [N.D.]), January 9, 1908", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn85042242/1908-01-09/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85042242/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn85042242"], "batch": ["ndhi_alamo_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1881", "description": ["Daily (except Monday) Began Apr. 18, 1881. -v. 36, no. 280 (Nov. 20, 1916). Available on microfilm from the State Historical Society of North Dakota, and the Library of Congress, Photoduplication Service. Archived issues are available in digital format as part of the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Weekly eds. : Bismarck tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1878), 1881-1884, and: Bismarck weekly tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1884), 1884-1916. Description based on: Vol. 8, no. 37 (Sept. 5, 1883). Bismarck tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1916) 2330-5967 (DLC)sn 85042243 (OCoLC)11987205"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:06.216Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-12", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-12"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85042242/", "image_url": [], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [46.805397, -100.783127], "location": ["north dakota", "bismarck", "burleigh", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-100.783127, 46.805397], "number": ["kansas state hist soc, newsp proj", "sn84022128", "2330-5924", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85042242/1916-11-20/ed-1/", "1", "sn85042588", "sn85042331", "5233", "state hist soc of n dakota", "2025-06-25t14:23:00", "11986756", "microfilm master", "2023-08-22t07:32:24.084270", "western rsv hist soc, newsp proj", "sn85042243", "online resource", "original", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85042242/1884-03-24/ed-1/", "western illinois univ", "sn85042242", "library of congress", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "microfilm service copy"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "chronicling america", "catalog", "bismarck daily tribune (bismarck, dakota [n.d.]) 1881-1916", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 60.992916, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["bismarck", "newspapers", "north dakota", "bismarck (n.d.)", "united states", "burleigh"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:15:53.161Z", "title": "Bismarck daily tribune", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn85042242/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218966/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1906", "dates": ["[1906 TO 9999]"], "description": ["Weekly Began in 1906. \"Beiblatt zu der Pierce County tribune.\" Place of publication varies: <1906>-Nov. 23, 1911, Rugby, N.D.; Dec. 7, 1911-Apr. 25, 1912, Devils Lake, N.D.; May 2, 1912-July 13, 1945?, Bismarck, N.D.; <Nov. 27, 1945>-, with an office in Bismarck, which moved to Fredonia, N.D. <Feb. 9, 1968>. Description based on: 1. Jahrgang, no. 37 (11. April, 1907); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed October 3, 2018). Latest issue consulted: 15. Jahrgang, no. 27 (19. Oktober 1920) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed October 3, 2018)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:44.751Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2018218966/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["german"], "location": ["omaha", "bismarck", "pierce", "fredonia", "north dakota", "ramsey", "united states", "douglas", "nebraska", "devils lake", "burleigh", "rugby", "logan"], "number": ["2639-5150", "online resource", "2018218966", "1055488809", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "der staats=anzeiger (rugby, north dakota) 1906-current [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 51.818283, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["rugby (n.d.)", "omaha", "bismarck", "logan", "pierce", "newspapers", "fredonia", "north dakota", "bismarck (n.d.)", "ramsey", "fredonia (n.d.)", "devils lake (n.d.)", "united states", "douglas", "devils lake", "burleigh", "rugby", "nebraska"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:56:24.792Z", "title": "Der Staats=Anzeiger", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2018218966/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218923/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1875", "dates": ["[1875 TO 1881]"], "description": ["Triweekly Began with November 15, 1875 issue. Ceased with April 16, 1881 issue? Weekly eds.: Bismarck weekly tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1875), 1875-1878, and: Bismarck tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1878), 1878-1881. Description based on: Vol. 5, no. 1 (June 4, 1877); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 21, 2013). Latest issue consulted: Vol. 5, no. 128 (April 9, 1878) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 21, 2013). Bismarck daily tribune (Online) 2330-5932 (DLC) 2013218925 (OCoLC)586060490"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:21.806Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218923/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["north dakota", "bismarck", "burleigh", "united states"], "number": ["online resource", "2013218923", "2330-5819", "849807600", "2013218925", "2013218924", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2013218927"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "bismarck tri-weekly tribune (bismarck, d.t. [n.d.]) 1875-1881 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["triweekly"], "score": 51.818283, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["electronic journals", "periodicals", "bismarck", "newspapers", "north dakota", "bismarck (n.d.)", "united states", "burleigh"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:48:24.858Z", "title": "Bismarck tri-weekly tribune", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2013218923/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218925/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1881", "dates": ["[1881 TO 1916]"], "description": ["Daily (except Monday) Began April 18, 1881; ceased with thirty-six year, no. 280 (November 20, 1916). Available on microfilm from the State Historical Society of North Dakota, and the Library of Congress, Photoduplication Service. Weekly eds.: Bismarck tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1878), 1881-1884, and: Bismarck weekly tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1884), 1884-1916. Description based on: Twentieth year (January 2, 1900); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 21, 2013). Latest issue consulted: Thirty-six year, no. 280 (November 20, 1916) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 21, 2013). Bismarck tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1916 : Online) 2330-5975 (DLC) 2013218926 (OCoLC)244293920"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:09.192Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218925/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["north dakota", "bismarck", "burleigh", "united states"], "number": ["2013218928", "online resource", "2013218923", "2330-5932", "2013218926", "2013218925", "586060490", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2013218927"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "bismarck daily tribune (bismarck, north dakota) 1881-1916 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 51.818283, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD AN", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["bismarck", "newspapers", "north dakota", "bismarck (n.d.)", "united states", "burleigh"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:48:24.858Z", "title": "Bismarck daily tribune", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2013218925/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218926/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1916", "dates": ["[1916 TO 9999]"], "description": ["Daily, <1982>- Began with thirty-sixth year, no. 281 (November 21, 1916). Sometimes published a morning edition and Sunday edition. \"Official newspaper for Bismarck and Mandan, N.D.\" Volume numbering irregular. Weekly ed.: Bismarck weekly tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1884), 1916-1943. Monthly ed.: Bismarck tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1943), 1943-1946. Thirty-sixth year, no. 281 (November 21, 1916); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 21, 2013). December 30, 1922 (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 21, 2013)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:05.616Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218926/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["bismarck", "north dakota", "united states", "morton", "mandan", "burleigh"], "number": ["2013218928", "online resource", "2013218926", "2013218925", "244293920", "2330-5975", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Bismarck daily tribune", "Bismarck evening tribune"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the bismarck tribune (bismarck, north dakota) 1916-current [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 51.818283, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["electronic journals", "periodicals", "bismarck", "newspapers", "north dakota", "bismarck (n.d.)", "united states", "morton", "mandan", "burleigh"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:48:24.858Z", "title": "The Bismarck tribune", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2013218926/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218927/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1878", "dates": ["[1878 TO 1884]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with vol. VI, no. 19 (October 9, 1878); ceased with vol. XI, no. 52 (May 30, 1884). Daily ed.: Bismarck daily tribune, 1881-1884. Triweekly ed.: Bismarck tri-weekly tribune, 1878-1881. Description based on: Vol. VI, no. 19 (October 9, 1878); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 21, 2013). Latest issue consulted: Vol. XI, no. 52 (May 30, 1884) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 21, 2013). Bismarck weekly tribune (Bismarck, N.D. : 1884 : Online) 2330-605X (DLC) 2013218928 (OCoLC)856527496"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:22.594Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2013218927/", "image_url": [], "index": 8, "language": ["english"], "location": ["north dakota", "bismarck", "burleigh", "united states"], "number": ["2013218928", "online resource", "2013218923", "2330-6017", "2013218925", "2013218924", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2013218927", "856524485"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Bismarck weekly tribune"], "p